<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_dbd4afc2839d.aspx"><b>小星</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsondbd4afc2839d">
嘒彼小星，三五在东。肃肃宵征，夙夜在公。寔命不同。<br />嘒彼小星，维参与昴。肃肃宵征，抱衾与裯。寔命不犹。
</div>
