<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_7b410a690ebe.aspx"><b>国风·邶风·旄丘</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson7b410a690ebe">
旄丘之葛兮，何诞之节兮。叔兮伯兮，何多日也？<br />何其处也？必有与也！何其久也？必有以也！<br />狐裘蒙戎，匪车不东。叔兮伯兮，靡所与同。<br />琐兮尾兮，流离之子。叔兮伯兮，褎如充耳。
</div>
